184
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,440
そうです。

185
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,440
はい。

186
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,440
「we're under attack」。

187
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,440
「we're under fire」。

188
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,440
うんうん。

189
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:11,440
はい。

190
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,720
